.SH "NAME"
liebert-esp2 \- Driver for Liebert UPS, using the ESP\-II serial protocol
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
\fBliebert\-esp2\fR \-h
.sp
\fBliebert\-esp2\fR \-a \fIUPS_NAME\fR [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.if n \{\
.sp
.\}
